<br>
Rough Trivial Levels for Monk Epic:<br>
<br>
Putrid Rib Bones in Qeynos hills: Level 9 Trivial<br>
Ghanex Drah's Head - Light blue to me at 22, so 24 is likely the last level to grab this item.  It's an uncommon drop so you may have to knock him off a few times.<br>
Dareb's Skull, Head of Shen - Hard to track down, but the mobs are roughly 20 to 24 so you should be safe to 30.<br>
Greater Light Stones - Level 18 at most.<br>
Dagger of Marnek/Blackened Wand - Both in Befallen of of 16-18ish mobs.  Absolute latest is level 24 to 27.  I wouldn't try 27 though.<br>
Blackened Sapphire - 28.  You'll need a good party and patience for this one, not to mention all the keys down there.<br>
Skull of Jhen'Tra - This one was the surprising one.  It was light blue to me at 22, though it might get higher level.  Try to get this one early if you can.<br>
Coronet of Buried Blood - No problems.  You'll be safe until 45.<br>
<br>
I think that's about it for headband/sash trivial levels.<br>
<br>
